component.name: AVCC0
component.description: Analog voltage supply pin. Connect this pin to VCC

component.name: AVSS0
component.description: Analog ground pin. Connect this pin to VSS

component.name: XCIN
component.description: Input pin for the sub-clock oscillator. Connect a crystal resonator between XCOUT and XCIN.

component.name: XCOUT
component.description: Output pin for the sub-clock oscillator. Connect a crystal resonator between XCOUT and XCIN.

component.name: RES
component.description: Reset signal input pin. The MCU enters the reset state when this signal goes low.

component.name: VCC
component.description: Power supply pin. Connect to the system power supply. Connect this pin to VSS through a 0.1-µF capacitor. Place the capacitor close to the pin.

component.name: VSS
component.description: Input Ground pin. Connect to the system power supply (0 V).

component.name: VCL0
component.description: Connect this pin to VSS through the smoothing capacitor used to stabilize

component.name: USBDP
component.description: D+ I/O pin of the USB on-chip transceiver. Connect this pin to the D+ pin of the USB bus

component.name: USBDM
component.description: D- I/O pin of the USB on-chip transceiver. Connect this pin to the D+ pin of the USB bus
